<br>
I am Xizor Pathfinder current Leader of The Menacing Horde. We have been watching the Lanys Coalition of Guilds since its inception. From afar, observing the growing pains from the beginning and even the old web message boards where initial interest was originally posted. Long ago we did not feel comfortable with the state of The Coalition. And as we were focussing on developing our own guild at the time did not want to get caught up in the chaos. HOWEVER we have seen many positive things happening over time and feel that the Coalition is now a viable community. Our Council voted on submitting an application and that passed so we then submitted this proposal to our Main body and it passed easily there as well.<br>
<br>
We are familiar with a few of the Member Guilds and their members and have grouped with them from time to time. We consider our closest ally to be Guardians of Dawn. And have many friends there. Some for great periods of time. <br>
<br>
Anyhow some basics about us. The Menacing Horde is about 50 Members strong currently and on a busy day we will have 14 to 16 on simultaneously. We also read in the By Laws of The Coaltions Charter that Guilds above 50 members are not eligable? Would this mean our Guild would have to remain stagnant at its current member base? Or that when we excceded that number that we would be cast out? This we will need to know as well please. <br>
<br>
We have a leadership Council of Seven Warlords ( The original founders of guild ) and an Officer pool of Eight Captains. <br>
As those of you who are familiar with us already our name does not imply we are evil. Just large enough not to be trifled with <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->    <br>
Our guild has been around just over a year. We believe in accepting Quality into our ranks before Quantity. And therefore have stringent and time consuming interview policies to weed out any prospects that might not be a good fit for our Family or end up doing the unthinkable and tarnishing the name of our proud guild.<br>
Ok enough info there for now. Our website is currently not online though will be in short order now. The address is <!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.geocities.com/jmerkdawg7">www.geocities.com/jmerkdawg7</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> <br>
We do however have our message boards running actively and that address is <!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://pub50.ezboard.com/bthemenacinghorde">pub50.ezboard.com/bthemenacinghorde</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
Please feel free to visit. Or say hello to any of The Menacing Horde that are on at any time. <br>
Thank you all,<br>
We look forward to hearing from you on this matter.<br>
<br>
 <p>Strength and Honor!!<BR>
<BR>
Warlord<BR>
Xizor Pathfinder<BR>
